data.description: Welcome home to quaint, desirable and fabulous Elmer, NJ.  This adorable bungalow is perfectly situated on a lightly traveled, quiet street in this family-friendly neighborhood.  It is in walking distance to town, yet has a farm-like feel sitting on just over 3/4 of an acre of newly split-rail fenced yard, perfect for the kiddos and fur babies.  You won't find this much ground  at this price in Elmer.  Main floor living space has a bright and spacious living room, formal dining room (currently used as child's playroom), great eat-in kitchen with newer appliances, large bathroom with new fixtures, and a separate laundry room with full-size washer/dryer.  This home is freshly painted and has original wood trims throughout, some hardwood floors, newer vinyl plank and brand new carpeting.  There are (2) large 2nd floor bedrooms with multiple walk-in closets, built-ins, and even a bonus, loft-type room that is the perfect office, den, gym or 3rd sleeping area.  There is also a full, dry basement perfect for additional storage.   This home has brand new electric service and a brand new Septic System sized for a 3-bedroom home if buyer chooses to expand in the future.  Cozy and efficient oil heat, and a brand new 2nd floor mini-split HVAC, add to this home's appeal .  There is also a huge 2-car detached, propane-heated garage with electric service, and (2) sheds offering even more storage.  Plenty of driveway parking as well.  So many possibilities for this fabulous home, or nothing to do at all and just move right in.  Don't let this one get away!
